TaskNest Main Menu Click within the note or task boxes to view the notes or tasks lists.
// Login Screen Like a nest for your mind Username Password Login
// Dashboard The Nest Task Name | Date | Something else Add Task View Tasks Display a list of notes Add Note View Notes Logout
